
1. Create shadow build directory.

2. Go into shadow build directory.

3. Ensure the correct DESTDIR is set in .pro file. This is the directory to which you want to install.

4. Run (assuming path to project is ../QMentat/):
qmake ../QMentat/QMentat.pro -r -spec linux-g++ CONFIG+=release

5. Run make

6. Run lrelease ../QMentat/QMentat.pro to generate .qm translation files.

6. Run make install

